 \forall s \in \mathbb{C} \setminus \{ 1 \}: \quad \zeta(s) = \frac{1}{1 - 2^{1-s}} \sum_{n=0}^{\infty} \left[ \frac{1}{2^{n+1}} \sum_{k=0}^{n} (-1)^{k} \binom{n}{k} (k + 1)^{-s} \right]. 
